name: Leaflet-jqslider-control
tagline: An example of how to add the JQSlider Control to a leaflet map.
body: I wanted to have a date slider that would control the data range shown on a leaflet map.  I found the nice JQSlider jQuery plugin and decided to give that a shot.  Seems to work pretty well!
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
